{"name":"Init.Data.Array.Attach","instances":[],"imports":["Init.Data.Array.Mem","Init.Data.List.Attach"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/Array/Attach.lean#L27-L27","name":"Array.attach","line":27,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/Array/Attach.html#Array.attach","doc":"`O(1)`. \"Attach\" the proof that the elements of `xs` are in `xs` to produce a new array\nwith the same elements but in the type `{x // x ∈ xs}`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Array/Attach.html#Array.attach\"><span class=\"name\">Array</span>.<span class=\"name\">attach</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(xs : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <span class=\"fn\">{ <span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span> // <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">xs</span></span> }</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/daa22187642d4cf6954c39a23eab20d8a8675416/src/Init/Data/Array/Attach.lean#L21-L23","name":"Array.attachWith","line":21,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/Array/Attach.html#Array.attachWith","doc":"`O(1)`. \"Attach\" a proof `P x` that holds for all the elements of `xs` to produce a new array\nwith the same elements but in the type `{x // P x}`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a cl